data.description: Welcome to this wonderful spacious Speedway ranch with a great location, walking distance to meadowood park, elementary school, and high school. Enjoy listening to the sound of the race cars on your front deck in the spring and summer. 2,500 square feet of space!! Three bedrooms and two and a half baths. Primary bedroom is roomy and has a nicely updated bath. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout the home. Bright formal living room with built in shelves, Large family room has space for dining table, wired for surround sound, lots of windows and sliding doors to the 12X7 glass enclosed porch with indoor/outdoor carpet, and access to huge fenced back yard and one and a half car garage. Kitchen with painted cabinets, pantry and space for a breakfast table and is open to the family room. Basement is a fantastic space with finished walls and newly painted floor that could be completed for a bedroom and a bonus space and bathroom that just needs tub hooked up or shower added. The possibilities are endless!
